{"tid":1682315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁蒙面法公聽會快將淪陷，手足必須盡快霸位齊反惡法","createTime":"2019-10-30T03:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T04:14:20.000Z","uid":283387,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"44805ba996b1880a3723ddb899814a59853706bd","tid":1682315,"uid":283387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"由於現時立法會禁止蒙面規例委員會中撐警議員佔大多數，正副主席都是盲目撐警議員，佢地勢必限制公聽會人數，甚至在公布公聽會的時間前已叫齊撐警撐人士霸晒所有位置，令反對禁蒙面法的市民無法在公聽會發聲，製造全民支持蒙面法的假象。<br />\n<br />\n到時出席公聽會的藍屍個個唱撐警歌，個個滿口歪理，都冇人可以阻止。我查到負責小組委員會秘書的電郵為psng@legco.gov.hk，大家請立即電郵給她，內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n「本人XXX(中英文名)將以個人名義出席公聽會表達本人對禁止蒙面規例的意見，本人願意於  貴委員會所訂的公聽會的任何一日的任何時間出席該公聽會，本人的電話為XXX，電郵為XXX，歡迎聯絡本人，謝謝」。<br />\n<br />\n大家必須以電郵發出，留下文字紀錄，同撐警撐黑人士鬥快霸位，表達對禁蒙面法的不滿。由於該等公聽會大多是在星期六進行，大家如無須在星期六返工，大可通知立法會秘書處可在任何一個星期六出席公聽會。<br />\n<br />\n如立法會在以下網址：<a href=\"https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/list.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2Flist.aspx&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt397g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=24c9bde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/list.aspx</a> 正式公布公聽會時間，大家可盡快將上述電郵再SEND多一次去公聽會的相關電郵或下載相關表格，填相關表格傳真或電郵回秘書處，盡快霸位，為因禁蒙面法而無辜被捕的手足發聲！"},{"pid":"f3f3f961659e635a52b0aacdab1bd69f5d87d8a2","tid":1682315,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b30792565afa449a6235abc06750027680e2250","tid":1682315,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f00ec9b8ab05691027da483d8c6e990ff74eaa9","tid":1682315,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d89a051c20d6395353dbbf81f8dc408539f1a8bf","tid":1682315,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6269a531dea17cd76d214e83ee253902355db0b","tid":1682315,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/Task1</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt397g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=8f6078e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"}]}